lead_paragraph: Third-seeded Agnieszka Radwanska came through a tough first set before beating Monica Niculescu 7-5, 6-1 on Wednesday to reach the quarterfinals of the Qatar Open.

headline.print_headline: Radwanska Beats Niculescu to Reach Doha Quarterfinals
headline.main: Radwanska Beats Niculescu to Reach Doha Quarterfinals
